* Integer Repeat Counter v 0.1
=================================================================

Release date: Feb 8, 2013
Authors: Mohammad Sadegh Rasooli 

This is a simple program to find repeated integers.

=================================================================
* Updates
=================================================================

v 0.1 - initial release Feb 8, 2013

=================================================================
* Requirements
=================================================================
The following items should be installed:

	* Python: http://python.org/

=================================================================
* USAGE
=================================================================
Usage:
	>> python findrepeats.py < [inputfile]
	* Example
		>> python findrepeats.py <  samplearray.txt 
	The  samplearray.txt  should look like this (Each inetger in one line):
		1
		3
		2
		1
		2
	The output should look like this:
		1 occured 2 time(s)
		2 occured 2 time(s)
		3 occured 1 time(s)


=================================================================
* WARNING
=================================================================
All the values in the stdin file should be integers (each integer in one line)

